data.title: The weather in February in Munka-Ljungby
data.meta_description: The average weather for the month of February in Munka-Ljungby. Read about the average temperatures and rainfall in Munka-Ljungby for February.
data.text:
Normal weather for Munka-Ljungby in February

It's cold in February in Munka-Ljungby with an average temperature of 4°C. Temperatures this month range from a low of 1°C to a high of 6°C. At night, you can expect temperatures between -5°C and 2°C.

In February, there is an average of 70 mm of precipitation, spread over 13 days days. Of the total precipitation, about 8,4 cm falls as snow in February. The wind speed is around 4 Bft, mostly coming from the South.

The UV index is a maximum of 3 this month. That's a moderate value on the intensity scale of 1 to 11. Unprotected skin can burn in about 30 minutes.
